International Corona Resources Ltd saidits board of directors believes that terms of Royex Gold MiningCorp's previously announced offer are fair and reasonable, butit decided it will make no recommendation on the offer to itsshareholders.    Royex on March 31 offered to buy four mln Corona shares.For each Corona share it offered four dlrs cash, one series Bshare of Royex, one series C share of Royex and one sharepurchase warrant. It also bid for all Corona warrants expiringAug 31, 1987. Reuter&#3;